{"article_id":"WZA1RHKEW7c3fC0k","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Sen. Mary Landrieu is looking for a win-win ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"as she pushes for a Senate vote","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to approve the long-delayed Keystone pipeline in a bid","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to deliver a victory for the energy industry","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"-- and for herself , in a tough runoff election next month .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"The senator is facing Republican Rep. Bill Cassidy","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"after being forced into the runoff .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Within hours of returning to Capitol Hill ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Landrieu called for a Senate vote on the Keystone bill ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"which is now teed up for next Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Republicans responded swiftly to Landrieu 's maneuvering ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"scheduling a vote in the House , likely for Friday , on an identical bill","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"sponsored by Cassidy .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"The back-and-forth amounts to a continuation of their bitter Senate campaign ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"with one of the most controversial energy projects in America caught in the middle .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"The TransCanada-built pipeline ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"which would cross over an aquifer in Nebraska ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"has been held up for six years by environmental and other concerns .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"White House spokesman Josh Earnest ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"traveling with President Obama in Burma ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"told reporters","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that the president takes a `` dim view '' of legislative efforts","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"to force action on the project .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Earnest stopped short of threatening a veto ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"but reiterated Obama 's preference","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"for evaluating the pipeline through a long-stalled State Department review .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Obama has repeatedly ordered such reviews under pressure from environmental groups ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"who say","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"the project would contribute to climate change .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"Landrieu ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"who is thought to be trailing Cassidy ahead of their Dec. 6 runoff election ,","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"wants to boost the energy industry","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"by pushing Keystone .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"The measure was one","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"she co-sponsored with Sen. John Hoeven , R-N.D. , back in May .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"\" We can pass the Keystone pipeline","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"and answer the frustrations of the American people , \"","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"\" So they could rest next","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"and say ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"oh my gosh","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"the senators of the United States of America have ears","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"and they have brains","depth":15},{"id":43,"text":"and they have hearts","depth":15},{"id":44,"text":"and they heard what we said","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"and we can do this . \"","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"Cassidy noted","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"that the House has passed pro-Keystone legislation eight times ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"and `` the Senate did not consider any of the eight . ''","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"After Landrieu called for a vote ,","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Cassidy and GOP leaders in the House said","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"they would vote on a Cassidy-authored Keystone bill .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"`` I hope","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"the Senate and the president do the right thing","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"and pass this legislation","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"creating thousands of jobs , ''","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Cassidy said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"`` After six years , it ' s time","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"to build . ''","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"The legislative tug-of-war came","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"a day","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"after aides first said","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"that Senate Democrats were considering bringing the pipeline to a vote","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"in order to boost Landrieu ahead of the runoff election .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"( The two rivals are heading to a runoff","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"because neither got more than 50 percent of the vote last week . )","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"The pipeline is a popular project in oil industry-heavy Louisiana ,","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"and Landrieu has touted her support of the pipeline and her tenure as chairwoman of the Senate energy committee in her campaign .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"On the Senate floor on Wednesday , Landrieu insisted","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"she was not trying to gain political points ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"she didn ' t even care","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"if her name stayed on the bill .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"\" I didn ' t come here","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"to see my name in lights , \"","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"\" I came to fight for jobs for my state . \"","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"She also seemed to take credit for Cassidy 's House bill ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"calling it `` identical '' to the legislation","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"she co-sponsored .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"However , Cassidy told Fox News ' Greta Van Susteren","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"that his rival 's assertion","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"that politics were not involved","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"was obviously untrue","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":".","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"`` I have to smile","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"when Sen. Landrieu says","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"politics are not involved , ''","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"he said on `` On the Record . '' `` Clearly","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"( Senate Majority Leader Harry )","depth":15},{"id":90,"text":"Reid did not care about the 40,000 jobs","depth":16},{"id":91,"text":"that would be created for families","depth":17},{"id":92,"text":"which are struggling ,","depth":17},{"id":93,"text":"but he does care about Sen. Landrieu ' s job .","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"So finally he is going to take the bill up .","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"I don ' t think","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"the president cares about those 40,000 people . ''","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"Senate Republicans and several moderate Democrats have pushed for the project to be approved for years ,","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"and backers of the project got a major win","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"after Republicans took control of the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"Supporters say","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"the construction of the pipeline would create tens of thousands of jobs .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Landrieu said in an evening press conference","depth":3},{"id":103,"text":"that she does not have a commitment from Obama","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"that he would sign the bill","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"should it reach his desk ,","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"but she is `` hopeful .","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"'' `` We believe","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"the bill","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"we drafted","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"could receive support in the House of Representatives","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"and get the president 's signature , ''","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"she said .","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"Landrieu is facing a tough battle","depth":4},{"id":114,"text":"to keep her job","depth":4},{"id":115,"text":"after nearly 20 years in office .","depth":3},{"id":116,"text":"A Real Clear Politics average of recent polls has the senator trailing her rival by nearly 5 points ahead of the election on Dec. 6 .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":233,"left":229,"right":232,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":229,"left":218,"right":228,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":218,"left":145,"right":217,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":123,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":121,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":0,"right":120,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":118,"right":119,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":122,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":125,"right":143,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":7,"right":124,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":132,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":127,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":10,"right":126,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":128,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":129,"right":17,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":136,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":134,"right":135,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":134,"left